n><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t<\/span>&lt;li&gt;We collect minimal data&amp;mdash;mainly your email (if you sign up), voting activity (stored anonymously), and basic technical information.&lt;\/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t<\/span>&lt;li&gt;We don&amp;rsquo;t sell your data, track your identity, or use third-party ads.&lt;\/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t<\/span>&lt;li&gt;Read our Privacy Policy for the full breakdown.&lt;\/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;\/ul&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;h2&gt;Cookies and Technology&lt;\/h2&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;We use cookies only for functionality, such as keeping you logged in and remembering your preferences. We don&amp;rsquo;t use them for advertising or creepy tracking.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"3825 characters\">&lt;p&gt;You can manage cookies through your browser at any time.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\